### Find your next favorite drop spot
The Vimaan(Plane) gets a visual makeover along with better overall visibility of the map from flight to spot your *favorite* areas faster. Also, now the high tier loot zones can be spotted easily with sky high beams, so take your chances dropping there, *if you must.* 

*In other news, some strange things can be seen floating over the skies of virlok, wonder what's that about..*

![enter image description here](https://i.imgur.com/fmyrFLI.gif)

### Geared up from Get go
Dropped in a 'dry' spot or too 'hot' of a spot? Fight or run your way out with the *new-but-old* default side-arm. 
